     A** BBBPP01 ***********************************************
     A* FILE NAME. : TOYOTA SYSTEM SUPPLY PART UNIT PRICE M/F *
     A* FILE ID. : BBBPP01. <PF>                               *
     A* CREATE DATE. : APR.17,'90.                             *
